### Global Search System - API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### 1. Unified Search - All Entities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search?query=javascript&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### 2. Unified Search - Specific Entities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search?query=react&entities=courses,questions&limit=3
Accept: application/json

### 3. Instant Search Suggestions (Autocomplete)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/suggestions?query=py
Accept: application/json

### 4. Course Search - Basic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/courses?query=web
Accept: application/json

### 5. Course Search - With Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/courses?query=development&skills=JavaScript,React&priceMin=0&priceMax=1000&level=intermediate&sortBy=popular
Accept: application/json

### 6. Course Search - Sort by Price
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/courses?query=&sortBy=price&page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### 7. Question Search - Basic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/questions?query=how to
Accept: application/json

### 8. Question Search - With Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/questions?query=&minVotes=5&hasAcceptedAnswer=true&sortBy=votes
Accept: application/json

### 9. Post Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/posts?query=hello&sortBy=newest
Accept: application/json

### 10. User Search - Basic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/users?query=john
Accept: application/json

### 11. User Search - Filter by Role
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/users?query=&role=instructor
Accept: application/json

### 12. Skill Swap Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/skill-swaps?query=&status=pending
Accept: application/json

### 13. Empty Query Test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search?query=
Accept: application/json

### 14. Pagination Test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search/courses?query=&page=2&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### 15. Invalid Entity Type (should fail gracefully)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/search?query=test&entities=invalid,courses
Accept: application/json
